Project:

This application contains Web API services used by the android application.

Model:

Vendor:
VName
VEmail

Customer:
CName
CEmail

Admin:
AName
AEmail

Offer:
VName
offer_startDate
offer_EndDate
Store
location id


REST API:

/GET_OFFER - based on location
/DELETE_OFFER - by Vendor/ADMIN
/UPDATE_OFFER - by Vendor/Admin
/ADD_OFFER - by Vendor/Admin
